Arsenal Rallies to Beat Barcelona 2-1 in Champions League; Shakhtar Wins

-- B y   B o b   B e n s c h
-- 
2011-02-16T21:36:52Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-02-16/arsenal-rallies-to-beat-barcelona-2-1-in-champions-league-shakhtar-wins.html
Arsenal came from behind to defeat
Barcelona 2-1 in the Champions League round of 16, as Shakhtar
Donetsk won 3-2 at Roma.    Robin van Persie  and Andrey Arshavin scored five minutes
apart in the second half to give Arsenal the win at the Emirates
Stadium in  London .  Jadson, Douglas Costa and Luiz Adriano had the goals as
Shakhtar won in  Italy .  Barcelona and Shakhtar will host the return matches in the
two-game series on March 8.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Bob Bensch at 
 bbensch@bloomberg.net  